{
  "stem": "15694.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she knew we wouldn't let her go, and the answer of-- and that's-- that's how-- that's how you-- you learned the psychology of this type of business.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were told.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to move all into one place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from the little villages, they were put into-- also into the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The villages were cleared, and everything went into the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, Bochnia was a small town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I can't say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no contact except we-- we said hello to the-- the person-- to the blacksmith opposite.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, we had no--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From what I've heard, there were-- there was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Personally, I haven't experienced--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As yet, there were no rewards for catching Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This comes later when we-- when there were rewards for catching Jews outside-- outside the ghettos, or those who possibly went on false papers as Aryans or non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If somebody-- some Poles found them and gave them away, they were given a kilo of sugar-- sugar, or some vodka, which was enough for them to betray us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, how much more crowded can it get?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Six people in-- in our room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But soon there was another-- the people of that bungalow had to give up another room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another little family came there, two adults and a girl about two years older than myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And well, this was quite a full house then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, when the ghettos were sold, you know, assigned, the rumors started flying that there were-- the Germans were sending special Einsatzgruppen, special groups, and they roamed from ghetto to ghetto and shot people at random.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, there were rumors of 50 dead there, and 50 there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
